OL,3,CWhy have England chosen Kansas City as
OL,4,Ctheir World Cup base?
OL,6,FBy US Correspondent Dan Rivers,
OL,7,Fadditional reporting by Washington
OL,8,FNews Editor Jonathan Wald
OL,10,FMany football fans might struggle to
OL,11,Ffind Kansas City on a map, but part of
OL,12,Fthe reason it has been chosen as
OL,13,FEngland's tournament base is simply
OL,14,Fthat it is in the centre of the United
OL,15,FStates.
OL,17,FIt means the players won't have to
OL,18,Fendure any gruelling coast-to-coast
OL,19,Fflights ahead of each match.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
