OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778868675
OL,3,CWhy have England chosen Kansas City as
OL,4,Ctheir World Cup base?
OL,6,FThe other argument for Kansas City,
OL,7,Fwhich straddles its eponymous state
OL,8,Fand neighbouring Missouri, is the
OL,9,Ftraining facilities it offers.
OL,11,FOr so England thought.
OL,13,FIn fact, Thomas Tuchel's boys have
OL,14,Flost their preferred base camp, at the
OL,15,FCompass Minerals National Performance
OL,16,FCentre, to their arch-rivals Argentina.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778868675
OL,3,CWhy have England chosen Kansas City as
OL,4,Ctheir World Cup base?
OL,6,FFIFA intervened and insisted the South
OL,7,FAmerican side could 'pull-rank' and
OL,8,Fuse the superior complex, since they
OL,9,Fare playing a fixture in Kansas City,
OL,10,Fwhile England is merely using the mid-
OL,11,Fwest city as a base.
OL,13,FIn terms of pitches, it's unlikely to
OL,14,Fmake any difference, since England's
OL,15,Ftraining ground offers similar well-
OL,16,Ftended lawns to Argentina's.
OL,18,FInside the buildings, though, it's
OL,19,Fanother story. Argentina's facility is
OL,20,Fprobably the best in America, if not
OL,21,Fthe world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778868675
OL,3,CWhy have England chosen Kansas City as
OL,4,Ctheir World Cup base?
OL,6,FDavid Beckham, while visiting,
OL,7,Freportedly told staff that he ranked
OL,8,Fit in the top three globally, and when
OL,9,Fpressed, couldn't name anywhere better.
OL,11,FIt features pressurised hyperbaric
OL,12,Fchambers, specialised swimming pools
OL,13,Fwith underwater treadmills, recovery
OL,14,Fbaths, motion capture cameras to
OL,15,Fassess player gait, a state-of-the-art
OL,16,Fgym, relaxation rooms with zero-
OL,17,Fgravity chairs, and much more.
OL,19,FEngland is hoping to recreate some of
OL,20,Fthese facilities at Swope Park to the
OL,21,Fsouth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778868675
OL,3,CWhy have England chosen Kansas City as
OL,4,Ctheir World Cup base?
OL,6,FThere are plans to borrow some
OL,7,Fequipment from the Compass Minerals
OL,8,Fcomplex, but it can't compete with the
OL,9,Fextraordinary building on offer to
OL,10,FArgentina.
OL,12,FEngland's advance party were
OL,13,Fundeterred by news their nemesis had
OL,14,Fsecured the training ground, telling
OL,15,Fstaff they had "fallen in love" with
OL,16,Fthe city and were determined to base
OL,17,Fthemselves there, even if it meant
OL,18,Freassessing their plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
