PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778868675
OL,3,CWhy have England chosen Kansas City as
OL,4,Ctheir World Cup base?
OL,6,FEngland will be staying at the Inn at
OL,7,FMeadowbrook, selected for its relaxing
OL,8,Fatmosphere and set within rolling
OL,9,Fparkland with picturesque lake views.
OL,11,FThe cafe and restaurant will be at the
OL,12,Fplayers' disposal for the duration of
OL,13,Ftheir World Cup journey.
OL,15,FSome residents are reportedly irked at
OL,16,Fthe disruption caused by increased
OL,17,Fsecurity around the hotel, especially
OL,18,Fas few have ever heard of any of the
OL,19,FEngland players.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
