FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778868675
OL,3,CWhy have England chosen Kansas City as
OL,4,Ctheir World Cup base?
OL,6,FIt does suggest, though, that the
OL,7,Fsquad will be able to wander the leafy
OL,8,Fstreets largely unnoticed by the
OL,9,Flocals.
OL,11,FThe England team also might have a
OL,12,Fchance to explore the centre of the so-
OL,13,Fcalled Paris of the Plains, which got
OL,14,Fits nickname from its rich jazz
OL,15,Fheritage and relaxed approach to
OL,16,FProhibition.
OL,18,FThe city is tranquil and green, with
OL,19,Freputedly more fountains than any
OL,20,Fother city apart from Rome.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778868675
OL,3,CWhy have England chosen Kansas City as
OL,4,Ctheir World Cup base?
OL,6,FThere is certainly less to distract
OL,7,Fthe team in terms of nightlife than
OL,8,Fother big American centres, perhaps
OL,9,Fexplaining why both England,
OL,10,FArgentina, the Netherlands, and
OL,11,FAlgeria have all elected to centre
OL,12,Ftheir tournament here.
OL,14,FThere is also a flourishing "soccer
OL,15,Fculture" in KC, as locals call it,
OL,16,Fwhich is trying to garner a reputation
OL,17,Fas the sport's powerhouse in America.
OL,26,@vD@]OUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
