FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778868675
OL,3,CWhy have England chosen Kansas City as
OL,4,Ctheir World Cup base?
OL,6,FIt already has a rich sporting history
OL,7,Fwith the Kansas City Chiefs NFL side
OL,8,Fwinning three of the last five Super
OL,9,FBowls.
OL,11,FThe relationship between star player
OL,12,FTravis Kelce and Taylor Swift has also
OL,13,Fsprinkled A-List stardust on this
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,FKansas City might be used to having
OL,17,Fsports legends in its midst, but this
OL,18,Fsummer it will be hosting some of the
OL,19,Fmost famous players in the world from
OL,20,Fthe 'other' football.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778868675
OL,3,CWhy have England chosen Kansas City as
OL,4,Ctheir World Cup base?
OL,6,FLionel Messi still hasn't formally
OL,7,Fconfirmed his attendance at the
OL,8,Ftournament, but Argentina's record
OL,9,Fgoal scorer is likely to be here.
OL,11,FThis will be a contest which will
OL,12,Frightly put Kansas City on the map for
OL,13,F'soccer' fans, even if right now the
OL,14,Fonly thing many England fans know
OL,15,Fabout Kansas is that it was the
OL,16,Ffictional home of Dorothy in The
OL,17,FWizard of Oz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
