OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778868675
OL,3,CWhy have England chosen Kansas City as
OL,4,Ctheir World Cup base?
OL,6,FThankfully, the tornado season is just
OL,7,Fabout over, clearing the way for a
OL,8,Fsweltering summer where high humidity
OL,9,Fand temperatures will test the
OL,10,Fendurance of all players, no matter
OL,11,Fhow many hyperbaric recovery sessions
OL,12,Fthey have enjoyed.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
